# Machine Learning models
# NOTE: We do NOT ignore the 'model/' directory here.
# Vercel, Render, and Hugging Face serverless environments require
# pre-trained model binaries to perform inference.
# Make sure to commit 'model/house_model.joblib', 'model/feature_names.joblib', and 'model/metrics.json'.
